text: Dominika Sobolska (born 3 December 1991) is a Belgian volleyball player. She was a member of the Belgium women's national volleyball team. She played at the 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2016 Montreux Volley Masters, 2019 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League, and 2019 Women's European Volleyball Championship. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian volleyball players
